{"tid":1498104,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[柴灣IVE入] 希望柴灣IVE學生全力支持92罷課","createTime":"2019-08-23T09:10:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T08:06:17.000Z","uid":168496,"like":55,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"d1004620f74bcad7203a8548e6f5f04c84877c2f","tid":1498104,"uid":168496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T09:10:56.000Z","msg":"我們是一班柴灣IVE學生，眼見特首林鄭月娥仍然未回應廣大市民的五大訴求，而且縱容警隊多次濫用暴力，企圖利用警隊解決政治問題，而且警隊過去多次對無差別攻擊市民的白衣人視若無睹，顯示香港警察已經徹底失控，泯滅人性，我們對此表示憤慨，而且他們的惡行不可原諒。<br />\n<br />\n我們一班普通學生曾聯絡柴灣IVE學生會，詢問他們會否主動在校內舉辦罷課集會或在學校設置連儂牆，但他們表示曾經詢問校方可否舉辦這些活動，但校方禁止他們作出任何政治表態，認為學生會這樣做是唆擺同學，我們認為這是剝削了同學表達自己意見的權利。<br />\n<br />\n因此，我們現在想召集一些志同道合，立場相同的同學，一起商討柴灣IVE可如何配合92罷課。<br />\n<br />\nTelegram Group: <a href=\"http://t.me/cwivestrike\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fcwivestrike&d=3B0aCwotxrbiSqfA1QWlAvsPRfgRtgRFNgQ5kFpanIU%3D&h=00be5060\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/cwivestrike</a>"},{"pid":"24138e86fa253b51619c480a493f855aea12a42b","tid":1498104,"uid":168496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T09:13:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"718073ab92b59ba3d7eda4f53654288415eabdce","tid":1498104,"uid":168496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T09:14:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b5bdf0aa4575af4b9008b6e5ff5660ef8260b6e5","tid":1498104,"uid":297966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T09:18:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"40651e46bb3398d607f824769fc283989aec71f3","tid":1498104,"uid":168496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T09:24:20.000Z","msg":"推爆佢！"},{"pid":"6bdb1637f758fcf663d272834302176a3326aa7f","tid":1498104,"uid":18530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T09:29:25.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e7ebf2a942bbc1f9a5d77cf167c3f13ee6fe0541","tid":1498104,"uid":168496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T09:31:47.000Z","msg":"記得share去比唔同既朋友呀！"},